c: 17
v: 44
t: "Gakunswejesyaga Jwalakwe mawunde nsano nagaŵili kwisa soni litaka ni yaili mwalakwemo, ni pangali chindu chilichose ikaŵeje chikunswejesyaga ni lumbili Lwakwe, nambo kuti ŵanganyammwe ngankumanyilila kaswejesye kao. Chisimu Jwalakwe juŵele Jwakutulala nnope ntima, Jwakululuka kusyene"